# ============================================================
# 📝 NOTES
# ============================================================
# 
# To check what Git will ignore:
#   git check-ignore -v <filename>
# 
# To stop ignoring a file:
#   git add -f <filename>
# 
# To see all ignored files:
#   git status --ignored
# 
# ============================================================
